{"tid":1433691,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近識咗個sporty嘅絲打，係咪主流都會揀游水踩單車同溜冰","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:37:25.000Z","uid":59569,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e22d9a5461d97625a901c47e3c5a20c3b74ea8f","tid":1433691,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:20:49.000Z","msg":"游水 我個人就麻麻哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踩單車 可以勁到甩尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溜冰 識向前唔識停 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見大交合難得嚟緊好好天<br />\n諗住毒撚勇敢約一次絲打<br />\n但又唔知做咩好，有冇巴絲俾吓意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我又冇泳鏡又冇頭盔同護墊<br />\n一次過買會唔會好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8300656d1b2a0c55c2600bd424a3dac95c7770be","tid":1433691,"uid":22310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"行山"},{"pid":"51fecd5ef547bebe3c883c2875fe62846efabbbd","tid":1433691,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"護墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2c8be5027ac056f4a7e8c2537c39e477a17503","tid":1433691,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8300656d1b2a0c55c2600bd424a3dac95c7770be","tid":1433691,"uid":22310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"行山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"淨係行過乜李好得唔得"},{"pid":"b556b7474b7eaf574da5ebaa508478e9a9399498","tid":1433691,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51fecd5ef547bebe3c883c2875fe62846efabbbd","tid":1433691,"uid":238801,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"護墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo